'From Squeak3.3alpha of 30 January 2002 [latest update: #4827] on 19 April 2002 at 8:44:38 am'!"Change Set:		GridOriginFix-nkDate:			16 April 2002Author:			Ned KonzThe grid spec origin was not working reliably on pasteup morphs; if you moved the pasteup morph the grid would shift.This change set fixes this problem."!!PasteUpMorph methodsFor: 'display' stamp: 'nk 4/16/2002 11:39'!drawOn: aCanvas	"Update and draw the turtleTrails form. See the comment in updateTrailsForm."	super drawOn: aCanvas.	(self griddingOn and: [self gridVisible]) ifTrue:		[aCanvas fillRectangle: self bounds fillStyle:			(self gridFormOrigin: self gridOrigin grid: self gridModulus background: nil line: Color lightGray)].	self updateTrailsForm.	turtleTrailsForm ifNotNil: [aCanvas paintImage: turtleTrailsForm at: self position].	(submorphs size > 0 and: [self indicateCursor]) ifTrue:		[aCanvas			frameRectangle: self selectedRect			width: 2			color: Color black].! !